p: All experiments were conducted with at least three biological repeats and each qRT-PCR reaction was performed with three technical repeats. Statistical analysis was performed by SPSS 26.0 software (SPSS Inc., Chicago, IL, USA). The relative expression levels of target genes are shown as the mean ± standard deviation (SD). One-way ANOVA was used to analyze the significant difference between the mean values by showing different letters at p < 0.05.
